<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Don&apos;t underestimate a 15 year old reader. When I was 12, I&apos;ve read Flowers in the Attic...this is nowhere close. If the 15 year old wants to read it..<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Don't underestimate a 15 year old reader. When I was 12, I've read Flowers in the Attic...this is nowhere close. If the 15 year old wants to read it...celebrate the fact that he or she can read.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
