              <span id="reviewTextContainer1007593259" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17518502465787470856">Should be a five star book and would have been with a good editor. As it stands Roth’s self-pleasuring digressions, his pedantic cataloging of sideshow detail kept spoiling it for me. Still a brilliant achievement but there were times when I wished Saul Bellow had written it.</span>

          </span>
