	<tr>
		<td>
		    <b>
          <a title="Goodreads România" class="actionLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/19562081-citeste-cu-mine-pastorala-americana-de-philip-roth-3-5-din-4-voturi">Goodreads România:</a>
